casebody.data:
Stridsberg, Appellant, v. GEICO General Insurance Company, Appellee.

[Cite as Stridsberg v. GEICO Gen. Ins. Co., Ill Ohio St.3d 1212, 2006-Ohio-5855.]

(No. 2005-2128 Submitted October 3, 2006 Decided November 29, 2006.) Roger C. Stridsberg, for appellant. Reminger & Reminger Co., L.P.A., Danny Merril Newman Jr., and Egan Patrick Kilbane, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Klatt, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur. William A. Klatt, J., of the Tenth Appellate District, sitting for Resnick, J.
